@startuml DFD_Level2_Pet_Management
!define RECTANGLE class

skinparam defaultTextAlignment center
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

' External Entity
actor "Pet Owner" as Owner <<External Entity>>

' Level 2 Processes for Pet Profile Management (2.0)
rectangle "2.1\nCreate Pet\nProfile" as CreatePet <<Process>>
rectangle "2.2\nUpdate Pet\nInformation" as UpdatePet <<Process>>
rectangle "2.3\nUpload Pet\nPhoto" as UploadPhoto <<Process>>
rectangle "2.4\nManage Health\nJournal" as ManageHealth <<Process>>
rectangle "2.5\nTrack Vaccinations\n& Medications" as TrackVacc <<Process>>
rectangle "2.6\nRecord Weight\n& Growth" as RecordWeight <<Process>>
rectangle "2.7\nDelete Pet\nProfile" as DeletePet <<Process>>

' Data Stores
database "D2: Pets" as D2 <<Data Store>>
database "D3: Health Journals" as D3 <<Data Store>>
database "D10: Vaccinations" as D10 <<Data Store>>
database "D11: Weight Records" as D11 <<Data Store>>
database "File Storage\n(Images)" as FileStorage <<Data Store>>

' Create Pet Flow
Owner --> CreatePet : Pet Details\n(name, species, breed, DOB, gender)
CreatePet --> D2 : Store Pet Record
CreatePet --> Owner : Pet Profile Created\n(pet_id)

' Update Pet Flow
Owner --> UpdatePet : Updated Details\n(pet_id, fields)
UpdatePet --> D2 : Update Record
D2 --> UpdatePet : Current Pet Data
UpdatePet --> Owner : Updated Profile

' Photo Upload Flow
Owner --> UploadPhoto : Pet Photo\n(pet_id, image)
UploadPhoto --> FileStorage : Store Image File
FileStorage --> UploadPhoto : Image URL
UploadPhoto --> D2 : Update Photo URL
UploadPhoto --> Owner : Photo Updated

' Health Journal Flow
Owner --> ManageHealth : Health Entry\n(symptoms, diagnosis, treatment)
ManageHealth --> D3 : Store Health Record
D3 --> ManageHealth : Previous Entries
ManageHealth --> Owner : Health History

ManageHealth --> D2 : Read Pet Info
D2 --> ManageHealth : Pet Details

' Vaccination Tracking Flow
Owner --> TrackVacc : Vaccination Info\n(vaccine, date, next_due)
TrackVacc --> D10 : Store Vaccination Record
D10 --> TrackVacc : Vaccination History
TrackVacc --> Owner : Vaccination Schedule\n+ Reminders

TrackVacc --> D2 : Link to Pet
D2 --> TrackVacc : Pet ID

' Weight Tracking Flow
Owner --> RecordWeight : Weight Measurement\n(pet_id, weight, date)
RecordWeight --> D11 : Store Weight Record
D11 --> RecordWeight : Weight History
RecordWeight --> Owner : Weight Trends\n+ Charts

RecordWeight --> D2 : Read Pet Info
D2 --> RecordWeight : Breed, Age for BMI

' Delete Pet Flow
Owner --> DeletePet : Delete Request\n(pet_id)
DeletePet --> D2 : Delete Pet Record
DeletePet --> D3 : Delete Health Records
DeletePet --> D10 : Delete Vaccinations
DeletePet --> D11 : Delete Weight Records
DeletePet --> FileStorage : Delete Photos
DeletePet --> Owner : Deletion Confirmed

note right of CreatePet
  Level 2 DFD: Pet Profile Management (2.0)
  
  Sub-processes:
  2.1 - Pet profile creation
  2.2 - Profile updates (breed, name, etc.)
  2.3 - Photo upload and management
  2.4 - Health journal entries
  2.5 - Vaccination and medication tracking
  2.6 - Weight and growth monitoring
  2.7 - Profile deletion (cascade)
  
  Features:
  - Multi-pet support per owner
  - Photo gallery with main display photo
  - Comprehensive health history
  - Vaccination reminders
  - Weight trend analysis
end note

note bottom of D2
  Pets table stores:
  - pet_id, owner_id, name
  - species, breed, date_of_birth
  - gender, color, microchip_id
  - photo_url, created_at
end note

note bottom of D3
  Health Journals table stores:
  - journal_id, pet_id, date
  - symptoms, diagnosis, treatment
  - veterinarian, notes
  - attachments (prescriptions, reports)
end note

note bottom of D10
  Vaccinations table stores:
  - vaccination_id, pet_id
  - vaccine_name, date_administered
  - next_due_date, veterinarian
  - batch_number, notes
end note

note bottom of D11
  Weight Records table stores:
  - record_id, pet_id, date
  - weight_kg, bmi_category
  - notes (ideal weight range)
end note

@enduml
